  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StanzaFilter

    public final class IQTypeFilter
extends FlexibleStanzaTypeFilter<IQ>
    A filter for IQ stanza(/packet) types. Returns true only if the stanza(/packet) is an IQ packet and it matches the type provided in the constructor.
